description: This file defines data models for a restaurant menu app, specifically the MenuItemModel and CartLine classes used to represent menu items and shopping cart items, respectively.

classes.name: MenuItemModel
classes.description: A data class representing a menu item/dish with properties like id, name, description, price, imageUrl, category, popularity, and rating. It includes a copyWith method for creating modified copies.

classes.name: CartLine
classes.description: An immutable class representing a line item in the shopping cart, containing a MenuItemModel and its quantity, with a computed property for line total.

methods.name: copyWith (of MenuItemModel)
methods.description: Creates a copy of the MenuItemModel with optional overrides for each property.

methods.name: copyWith (of CartLine)
methods.description: Creates a copy of the CartLine with optional modifications for item and quantity.
